## temp_metric — Phase Overview

> **Full spec and logic details live in `scripts/temp_metric/for_temp_metric.txt`.**
> That file is the source of truth for phase definitions, rules, and thresholds rationale.
> When the logic changes, update that file first, then reflect it in the code.

### Implementation

| Phase | Function | File |
|-------|----------|------|
| Phase 1 — Feature Engineering | `compute()` | `src/model_monitor/metrics/temp_metric.py` |
| Phase 2 — Grading | `grade()` | `src/model_monitor/metrics/temp_metric.py` |

Thresholds: `configs/thresholds.yaml` → `metrics.temp_metric.grading`

Output statuses: `PASS` / `WARNING` / `FAIL` with a `reason` string.

### Results Layout

```
data/results/group_{id}/{date}/
    {id}_{date}_temp_metric.parquet          ← per-sensor results + status + reason
    {id}_{date}_temp_metric_summary.parquet  ← mean metrics + grade counts per hive_size
data/results/temp_metric_results.parquet     ← all groups/dates combined
```

