## temp_metric Skill Layout (`skills/temp_metric/`)

Each skill is a self-contained end-to-end pipeline. See `skills/temp_metric/README.md` for full details.

```
skills/temp_metric/
  spec/for_temp_metric.txt      ← source of truth: logic, rules, thresholds rationale
  config/extraction_plan.py     ← 51 groups, 643 dates, model names (from ground truth CSV)
  scripts/pull_samples.py       ← Step 1: Athena → local Parquet
  scripts/run_temp_metric.py    ← Step 2: compute + grade → result Parquet
```

**Run order:**
```bash
source scripts/refresh_aws_credentials.sh
nohup python skills/temp_metric/scripts/pull_samples.py > pull_log.txt 2>&1 &
python skills/temp_metric/scripts/run_temp_metric.py
```
